OL,3,CSolicitor jailed after stealing
OL,4,C#84,000 from elderly clients
OL,6,FA solicitor from Swindon has been
OL,7,Fjailed after admitting she abused her
OL,8,Fposition to steal tens of thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds from two vulnerable people.
OL,11,FAlison Griffiths, 55, of Sheerwold
OL,12,FClose, Stratton, Swindon, appeared at
OL,13,FSwindon Crown Court after pleading
OL,14,Fguilty to two counts of fraud by abuse
OL,15,Fof position.
OL,17,FShe was sentenced to 24 months in
OL,18,Fprison.
