OL,3,CSolicitor jailed after stealing
OL,4,C#84,000 from elderly clients
OL,6,FBetween December 2018 and February
OL,7,F2021, Griffiths stole around #49,000
OL,8,Ffrom a 94-year-old woman over whom she
OL,9,Fhad power of attorney, transferring
OL,10,Fmoney from the victim's account to her
OL,11,Fown and using the victim's account to
OL,12,Fwithdraw substantial sums from cash
OL,13,Fmachines.
OL,15,FThis was reported to police in April
OL,16,F2021 after Griffiths admitted to her
OL,17,Femployer that she had stolen from the
OL,18,Fvictim.
