OL,3,CSolicitor jailed after stealing
OL,4,C#84,000 from elderly clients
OL,6,FDuring the investigation into this
OL,7,Foffence, officers received a second
OL,8,Freport of fraud against the suspect.
OL,9,FBetween May 2020 and September 2021,
OL,10,FGriffiths took advantage of another
OL,11,Fvictim, an 80-year-old man who passed
OL,12,Faway in May last year.
OL,14,FAgain while acting as power of
OL,15,Fattorney, Griffiths transferred
OL,16,Fsubstantial sums of money from the
OL,17,Fvictim's account into her own, to the
OL,18,Famount of around #35,000.
